		"Pendapatan Docking Facility (MS)"   &amp; "," &amp;
		"Pendapatan Marine Logistik (MS)"   &amp; "," &amp;
		"Pendapatan Other Marine Service (MS)"   &amp; "," &amp;
		"Pendapatan Stuffing (DEPO)"   &amp; "," &amp;
		"Pendapatan Stripping (DEPO)"   &amp; "," &amp;
		"Pendapatan Penumpukan (DEPO)"   &amp; "," &amp;
